Combine artichokes, peppers, cheese and pepperoni in bowl. Add dressing; mix lightly. Refrigerate at least 1 hour. Can be overnight. Before serving, cut lettuce in half. Rinse; drain well. Place one half on plate, cut side down. Cut remaining lettuce into 1 inch chunks. Thread lettuce chunks and remaining ingredients alternately onto skewers. Drizzle with dressing remaining in bowl. Insert skewers into lettuce half.